Meet Britta Dyer—California State Director of American Forests and Coreen Francis—State Forester.

Arhaus has proudly partnered with American Forests, the nation’s oldest conservation organization, since 2017. Together, we’ve planted 130,000 trees to date—and we’re growing toward one million every day.

Follow Arhaus Admires, as we celebrate people who inspire us—their stories, their projects, and their own words.
